Dear Hiring Team,

I am writing to apply for the *Software Engineer - Implementation* role with *Just Appraised*. My background is in backend systems, integrations, and production automation: at Sperse I built a *Python*, *LangGraph*, *LangChain*, and *FastAPI* CRM platform serving 10,000+ users across 40+ specialized sub-agents, created a *FastMCP* server exposing 160+ backend actions, and wired *GitHub Actions* *CI/CD* with OpenTelemetry trace-based evals to catch latency, accuracy, and safety regressions before release. That work maps closely to your implementation needs around system integration, production reliability, and owning technical solutions end to end.

